## So sánh: V2 vs @BallisticEdge08

| Yếu tố | @BallisticEdge08 | V2 (thiết kế) |
|---------|:---:|:---:|
| Spec density | ~4 specs/chapter | ≥5 specs/chapter (data_density rule) |
| Physical Translation | 1 per chapter | ≥2 per chapter |
| Opening variety | 6 patterns (natural rotation) | 6 patterns (outline-controlled) |
| Heritage nugget | Always present | Conditional (need origin_history) |
| Transition quality | Excellent — always teases next product | Required — `ends_with` from outline |
| Weakness/con | ❌ Rarely mentioned | ✅ Mandatory per chapter |
| Source tagging | N/A | ✅ transcript / ai_knowledge |
| Myth debunking | Frequent but unstructured | ✅ Structured via `myths_misconceptions` |
